* dut-leasing
Lease Device Under Test
** Purpose
- Provide remote access to Device Under Test
- Allow others to access Device Under Test when not in use
** Concept
#+BEGIN_SRC ditaa :file concept.png
+----------------+     +-------------+     +---------+     +------+
| Target Manager |     |             +<--->+ Network +<--->+      |
+---------+      +<--->+ Test server |     +---------+     | User |
|   DUT   |      |     |             +<===>+   VPN   +<===>+      |
+---------+------+     +-------------+     +---------+     +------+
#+END_SRC

#+RESULTS:
[[file:concept.png]]

Terms explained on https://elinux.org/Test_Glossary
** Example
#+BEGIN_SRC ditaa :file example.png
+--------------+     +----------------+     +----------+     +-------------+
|   [Dryad]    | SSH |    [Boruta]    +<--->+ Internet +<--->+   [leszy]   |
|              +<--->+                |     +----------+     |             |
| Orange Pi R1 |     | Raspberry Pi 4 +<===>+ OpenVPN  +<===>+ Workstation |
+------+-------+     +----------------+     +----------+     +-------------+
       ^
       | SSH
       v
   +---+----+
   | [DUT]  |
   |        |
   | Pine64 |
   +--------+
#+END_SRC

