[[file:example.png]]

** Software
| Machine        | Operating system        |
|----------------+-------------------------|
| Raspberry Pi 4 | Raspberry Pi OS Desktop |
| Orange Pi R1   | Armbian Focal           |
| Pine64         | Armbian Focal Desktop   |
** Network
| Machine        |     WAN address | WAN source                   |   LAN address | LAN source |
|----------------+-----------------+------------------------------+---------------+------------|
| Raspberry Pi 4 |               ? | Provider DHCP                |   192.168.1.1 | Static     |
| Orange Pi R1   |     192.168.1.x | Test server DHCP             | 192.168.100.1 | Static     |
| Pine64         | 192.168.100.100 | Target manager DHCP (single) |           N/A | N/A        |
